stimulus: Welcome to the experiment. Press any key to begin.

You will see a list of words and colored squares in the following task.

Press the spacebar whenever you see a GREEN square.

Do not press a key if the square is RED

Press the spacebar to continue.

Please try to remember as many of the words as you can, and try to think about the meaning of each word as it appears.

After the detection and encoding task you will be asked to solve some math problems for 24 seconds.

Please solve as many problems as you can in the time given.

After solving the math problems, you will be asked to type in as many words

from the previous list as you can remember for 75 seconds.

If you finish recalling before the 75 seconds are up,

just sit tight and try to think of any more words you could have missed.
